{"tid":1994290,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[Bioweapon生化武器]研究:基因影響感染新型冠狀病毒病徵","createTime":"2020-04-29T11:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T11:16:24.000Z","uid":76705,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7ee40ede15be40a3673b718d1570fc5144cfddfb","tid":1994290,"uid":76705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T11:00:38.000Z","msg":"2600多對孖生兄弟姊妹中，部分是同卵雙胞胎，擁有完全相同的基因；部分則是異卵雙胞胎，基因有差異。研究人員將他們是否同住或有否接觸納入考慮因素，比較同卵和異卵雙胞胎病徵有多相似，結果發現出現不同病徵五成因素是來自基因。<br />\n<br />\n最受基因影響的病徵包括發燒、肚瀉、急性精神昏亂、失去味覺和嗅覺；相反，與基因無關的病徵包括咳嗽、聲沙、無胃口、胸口和腹痛等。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>領導今次研究的教授形容這個病毒「很奇怪」，不同人口的病徵有差異，並非隨機出現，亦非取決於你接觸過誰或居住在哪兒，而是有先天因素。他相信一個人的染病機率以至病情的輕重，某程度上由基因控制</strong></span>。<br />\n高度針對Gene group嘅病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=389237\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D389237&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw34WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=fd790a8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D389237&h=9020c1e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=389237</a>"},{"pid":"fef9bbb90dc8b5c517f6c687e4e19bdaa2069184","tid":1994290,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T11:02:31.000Z","msg":"X-men"},{"pid":"d70017cc4379c110926bcbfb1849b4b153f4ef3f","tid":1994290,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T11:16:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qwQrGiji0iY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqwQrGiji0iY&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw34WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=16710f0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qwQrGiji0iY</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\